Attribute & Description
1 	android:id -ID
2 	android:baselineAligned ( "true" or "false")
3 	android:baselineAlignedChildIndex
4 	android:divider (color value, in the form of "#rgb", "#argb", "#rrggbb", or "#aarrggbb".)
5 	android:gravity( top, bottom, left, right, center, center_vertical, center_horizontal etc)
6 	android:orientation ("horizontal" "vertical" )
7 	android:weightSum
-------------------
